debo ser ahora.

729
00:39:58,021 --> 00:39:59,021
Brooks Rattigan.

730
00:39:59,647 --> 00:40:01,024
El decano está listo.

731
00:40:04,986 --> 00:40:05,986
Hola.

732
00:40:06,529 --> 00:40:07,655
- ¡Oye!
- ¿Sí?

733
00:40:08,197 --> 00:40:09,449
Lo harás genial.

734
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:11,700
A menos que...

735
00:40:12,201 --> 00:40:13,411
